1
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:14,840
Darn it

2
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:15,880
What do we do?

3
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:17,320
Meeting adjourned.

4
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:18,920
Let's go.

5
00:00:18,920 --> 00:00:19,360
Yu Tong.

6
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,280
That's a beautiful name.

7
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:22,680
Un... Untie her.

8
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:23,160
Stay put.

9
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:24,040
General.

10
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:25,520
Strategist.

11
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:26,800
Brother.

12
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:28,080
Sister.

13
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:30,240
I'll say a few words first.

14
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:31,880
I'll just make two points.

15
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:32,960
Point number one.

16
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:35,160
Let's give a warm round of applause

17
00:00:35,160 --> 00:00:36,160
to welcome Yu Tong

18
00:00:36,160 --> 00:00:37,760
to our big family.

19
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:38,760
Welcome, welcome.

20
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:39,880
A warm welcome.

21
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:42,120
Point number two.

22
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:44,120
There were some misunderstandings before.

23
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:44,840
So,

24
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:45,760
those who should apologize...

25
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:47,080
should take the initiative to do so.

26
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:48,600
Then we can turn the page.

27
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:50,720
Wei Qiao.

28
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:51,360
Apologize.

29
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:52,280
It wasn't me.

30
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,920
I saw the Strategist pointing at you.

31
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:54,600
What's that supposed to mean?

32
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:55,520
I'll go first.

33
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:57,960
I'd like to apologize to everyone.

34
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:58,600
Earlier...

35
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,400
I caused everyone...

36
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,560
a lot of trouble.

37
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:02,560
Yu Tong is so magnanimous.

38
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:04,120
Your noble character...

39
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,840
shines like gold.

40
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:06,720
Enough.

41
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:07,800
Strategist.

42
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:09,000
Watch your boundaries.

43
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:11,480
Sister Aqin.

44
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,920
There were many misunderstandings before.

45
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:14,560
I hope we get along in the future.

46
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,840
Sister, why be so hypocritical?

47
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:28,680
You didn't say anything when I was weaving rope to catch you.

48
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,280
You just had to say in front of everyone

49
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,040
that you wanted to help catch the bad guys.

50
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:34,120
You're just trying to make me look bad.

51
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:36,320
You guys drink.

52
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:42,720
Now that Yu Tong has been cleared of suspicion,

53
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:43,560
then...

54
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,280
then...

55
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,400
there are no spies left.

56
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,480
Originally, it was just the three of us, right?

57
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:49,480
You,

58
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,040
me,

59
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:50,640
Qiao.

60
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:51,880
Later, ever since

61
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:53,920
Yu Tong and Aqin arrived,

62
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:55,280
there's been a spy in the team.

63
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:55,760
Right?

64
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:56,160
Right.

65
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:58,800
Now that Yu Tong is no longer a spy,

66
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,400
then...

67
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,920
Then there are no spies!

68
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,000
Are you stupid?

69
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:05,120
Since Yu Tong isn't the spy,

70
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:06,880
then Aqin must be the spy.

71
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:08,440
Strategist.

72
00:02:08,760 --> 00:02:09,880
That is your sister-in-law.

73
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,120
That is my fiancée.

74
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,000
Are we still brothers or not?

75
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:15,120
This isn't about being brothers!

76
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,440
Fine, fine, fine, fine.

77
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,040
Aqin

78
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:18,720
is a spy.

79
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:19,280
Right?

80
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:19,840
Look,

81
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,760
I'm also a spy.

82
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:21,960
Qiao is also a spy.

83
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:23,000
Only you are a good person.

84
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,520
Happy now?

85
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:24,600
The Lord is a spy too.

86
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:25,360
Is that okay?

87
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,520
You, just for Aqin's sake,

88
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,800
you dare say the Lord is a spy?

89
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:28,640
What do you mean "us"?

90
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:29,360
Just for a woman,

91
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,640
you say we're all spies?

92
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,280
And only you are a good person?

93
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,200
Isn't that normal?

94
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,320
Normal what? What's with your attitude?

95
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:33,960
Don't talk to me.

96
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,720
Turn around.

97
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,680
What are you doing? What are you doing?

98
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:36,800
Look at me.

99
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,880
I'll count to three, you get down here.

100
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,240
I won't come down even if you count to three hundred.

101
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,120
One, two, three.

102
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:41,800
Come on, come on.

103
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,560
Your counting doesn't count.

104
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,240
Two point five.

105
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:43,760
Who is it?

106
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,880
So noisy early in the morning.

107
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:45,960
Do you have no public morality?

108
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:46,800
Get lost!

109
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:49,200
Quick, quick, quick!

110
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,880
Was that He Ba and He Jiu who just passed by?

111
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,680
Yes!

112
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:55,120
Chase them! Chase them!

113
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,080
Stop chasing, stop chasing.

114
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,720
Being young is great.

115
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,080
Yeah.

116
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,000
They run so fast.

117
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,600
Stop targeting me.

118
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:05,440
If it weren't for you being fat,

119
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:06,640
we would have caught them long ago.

120
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,480
About this...

121
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,240
we can't tell Wei Qiao.

122
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,080
Strategist,

123
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:17,080
since we can't find the vat anyway,

124
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,360
and we can't get out,

125
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:20,800
who the spy is...

126
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,840
is it that important?

127
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:22,600
You're right.

128
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,120
Let's live in the moment.

129
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:27,240
Let's consider our major life events.

130
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,640
It's a deal then.

131
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,640
No more targeting Aqin.

132
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:38,080
Then you can't keep suspecting Yu Tong either.

133
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,680
You keep protecting Yu Tong.

134
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,120
Do you have feelings for her?

135
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,960
Then why have you been avoiding Aqin lately?

136
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,680
Both of you are...

137
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,680
Am I avoiding her?

138
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,560
She has such high Kung Fu.

139
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,360
If we really get out someday,

140
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,720
I won't have the face to see my brothers.

141
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,120
No fighting in the village!

142
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:04,000
I said, no fighting!

143
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,480
Help!

144
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,360
You two

145
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:11,440
Don't let it happen again

146
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,240
I'll let you off this time

147
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,240
Get out

148
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,240
What is it now?

149
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,160
Ask Sister Aqin

150
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,960
Ever since I got here,

151
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,640
she's been targeting me.

152
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,560
I don't know why.

153
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:29,320
I saw you let He Qi go.

154
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,400
I came out and found

155
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,720
He Qi was gone.

156
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,000
You were the only one in the yard.

157
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,320
You're slandering me!

158
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,400
Are you okay?

159
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,240
My mistake.

160
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,600
Stop fighting, stop fighting!

161
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:47,120
Where is Wei Qiao?

162
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:48,920
He was just here.

163
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,280
If he's not here,

164
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,720
then he's the one who let He Qi go.

165
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,480
Agreed.

166
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,120
Problem solved.

167
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:53,920
All good.

168
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:58,080
Your Village rules...

169
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,360
is there really only one?

170
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,160
That's right.

171
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:02,240
Centuries ago, our ancestors

172
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:04,080
came here to escape the war.

173
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,320
Perhaps they hated war so much,

174
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,720
that there is only this one rule:

175
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:08,840
No fighting.

176
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,800
Your voice sounds so nice.

177
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,760
Say it again.

178
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,480
No.

179
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,560
Just say it once more.

180
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:17,640
No.

181
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:19,760
Please.

182
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:26,000
Brother Yuwen.

183
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:28,360
I've caused you trouble again.

184
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:31,240
That Aqin is always targeting me.

185
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,400
I don't mind the trouble.

186
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,520
But if she targets you again,

187
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:36,840
just stay away from her.

188
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,120
She's so skilled in martial arts.

189
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,480
What if she hurts you?

190
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,040
She probably can't hurt me.

191
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,000
Why are you being so stubborn?

192
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,080
Because...

193
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:47,080
I remembered...

194
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,400
I know Kung Fu.

195
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,600
Then I know Kung Fu too.

196
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,480
You do?

197
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:56,800
I know how to waste time.

198
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,560
I'm serious.

199
00:05:59,360 --> 00:05:59,880
Alright.

200
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,960
Sure, sure, sure.

201
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,800
You don't believe me, do you?

202
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,160
I believe you, I believe you.

203
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,240
You just don't believe me.

204
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:08,960
If you don't believe me, try me.

205
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,440
You asked for it.

206
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,360
I'm going to make my move.

207
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,880
Don't blame me if I hurt you.

208
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,160
Starving Tiger Pounce!

209
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:24,880
Strategist?

210
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:25,720
What are you playing at?

211
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:30,360
Get up, get up!

212
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:31,720
Easy, easy, easy.

213
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,280
Are you okay?

214
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,000
Strategist.

215
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,960
Take care of your body.

216
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:37,720
Get out!

217
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,560
Sorry.

218
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,720
I hit too hard.

219
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,480
Strategist.

220
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,440
Keep it down.

221
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,040
Don't.

222
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,560
Yu Tong, you're really amazing.

223
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,640
Yeah.

224
00:06:58,160 --> 00:07:00,560
But we don't know just how amazing.

225
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,600
If only we could find a villain to test it on.

226
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,200
How about we...

227
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:07,720
...do something bad?

228
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,520
What exactly should I give?

229
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:16,440
Flowers.

230
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,760
Why give flowers?

231
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,480
Too tacky.

232
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,000
You should just...

233
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,520
...give your most precious possession.

234
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:22,560
I only have three precious things.

235
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,360
My precious saber, my brothers, and myself.

236
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,240
So what do I give?

237
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,080
The saber.

238
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:26,720
The saber?

239
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,480
I'm the type of person...

240
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,160
...where man and saber are inseparable.

241
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,080
If I give the saber...

242
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,000
...and she actually accepts it...

243
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:32,760
...then what do I do?

244
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:34,280
You're the one insisting on giving it.

245
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,600
Then later when I charge into battle...

246
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,520
...I'll wield you to kill?

247
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,520
No way.

248
00:07:39,880 --> 00:07:40,520
The rest...

249
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:41,920
...are my brothers and myself.

250
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:47,560
Big Brother...

251
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,840
In principle, I'd rather not...

252
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:50,800
What are you thinking?

253
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,520
I mean...

254
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:55,160
...I want to give myself to her.

255
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,600
Isn't that a bit too fast?

256
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,440
You call this fast?

257
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:59,040
Didn't you see the Strategist and Yu Tong?

258
00:07:59,040 --> 00:07:59,760
They've already...

259
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,600
No.

260
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,800
I can't fall behind.

261
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:04,600
So you're courting her...

262
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,800
...just so you don't fall behind?

263
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:07,120
You don't understand.

264
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:08,960
I'll just give myself.
